{"article_id":"0EVaEvxcbX8Yvsn9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Despite nearly a year 's worth of heartache ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Republicans ca n't quit trying to repeal Obamacare .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Senate Republicans plan to include a repeal of the individual mandate","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"-- a key piece of the Affordable Care Act --","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"in their tax reform efforts .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"It 's a move","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that dramatically raises the stakes for President Donald Trump and congressional Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"who are still looking for a single , substantial legislative accomplishment","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to deliver to the American people this year .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"For Republicans , the benefits are tempting .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"If they can pull it off ,","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"it 's a two-for-one victory .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"They will have overhauled the US tax code","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"and taken a bite out of former President Barack Obama 's signature legislative achievement ,","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"even if it falls short of the `` root and branch '' health care repeal","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"many had vowed to see through .","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"if they fail ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"Republicans will enter the midterm election year with their message muddled ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"without a victory on tax reform ,","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"and having spent a year 's worth of time","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"trying and repeatedly failing to dismantle Obamacare with nothing","depth":16},{"id":23,"text":"to show for it","depth":16},{"id":24,"text":"but bad headlines .","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"One Senate Republican , Susan Collins of Maine , warned her fellow party members to be wary of diving back into the health care fight","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and risk capsizing their tax reform efforts","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"just as they were making progress .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` I personally think","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that it complicates tax reform , ''","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Collins told reporters","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"as she left a GOP lunch Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Repealing the individual mandate has been up for consideration for weeks ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"but the discussion had been happening mostly behind the scenes","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"as Republicans debated using an estimated $ 338 billion in savings","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to cover the cost of and finance additional tax cuts over the next decade .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"The mandate requires nearly all Americans to have health insurance","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"or pay a penalty .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"But getting rid of it has a cost .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Roughly 4 million fewer people would be covered in the first year","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"the repeal would take effect ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"the Congressional Budget Office said last week ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"rising to 13 million by 2027 ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"as compared to current law .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Premiums would also rise by about 10 % in most years of the decade ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"CBO said .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Monday morning , President Donald Trump tweeted from a trip to Asia","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that he wanted to see the repeal of the individual mandate included .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"I am proud of the Rep. House & Senate","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"for working so hard on cutting taxes { & reform . }","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"We 're getting close !","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Now , how about ending the unfair & highly unpopular Indiv Mandate in OCare","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"& reducing taxes even further ?","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Cut top rate to 35 %","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"w/all of the rest going to middle income cuts ?","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"November 13 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Senate leaders and many House rank-and-file members appear to have embraced the position .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"`` We had to get our members to where they were comfortable with it ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"and I think","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"we are there , ''","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"said Sen. John Thune , a Republican from South Dakota and member of GOP leadership .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"`` It just makes the overall bill a lot more possible , ''","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"said Sen. Roger Wicker , R-Mississippi .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Introducing a repeal of the individual mandate into the tax debate , however , is a risky proposition for Senate Republicans","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"who failed to repeal the mandate in July","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"after three Republicans","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"-- Collins , Sen. John McCain and Lisa Murkowski --","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"all voted against it","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Even lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"who embraced repealing the individual mandate","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"were keenly aware of the danger","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"it could pose to their delicately crafted tax bill .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"After all , trying to re-write the health care law had proven to be a massive flop for Senate Republicans , a failure","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that has echoed across conservative talk radio","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"and hurt the GOP with their donor class .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"`` I have some concern","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"about mixing health care with taxes","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"because the health care issues have been so difficult , ''","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"said Sen. John Kennedy , a Republican from Louisiana","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"who supports repealing the individual mandate as part of the tax bill .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"`` But , it 's really not health care","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"that we are talking about .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"We are talking about tax . ''","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"A key driver of the Senate Republicans ' decision Tuesday was simple arithmetic :","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"They need the money .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"As it stands now ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"their tax plan increases the deficit outside the 10-year window","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"and that is against Senate rules","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"if lawmakers want to use a process","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"that allows them to pass the tax bill with just a simple majority .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"`` Whatever people want to do is fine with me .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"My concern is that we not generate deficits ,","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"so if it is something","depth":17},{"id":95,"text":"we could use","depth":19},{"id":96,"text":"to buffer","depth":20},{"id":97,"text":"-- especially during the first 10 years --","depth":20},{"id":98,"text":"deficits ,","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"then I 'd be open to it , ''","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"Tennessee Republican Sen. Bob Corker said .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"`` As long as it 's real .","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"I know","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"some people think","depth":16},{"id":104,"text":"it is a gimmick .","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"I want to look into it more fully . ''","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"For now , Republican senators","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"who voted against the repeal of the individual mandate in July ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"are n't coming out against the latest plan as of Tuesday evening .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"McCain and Murkowski have said","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"they are both still examining the newest proposal ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"with McCain said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"he was leaning toward supporting it","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Obamacare repeal :","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Watch McCain vote no","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Obamacare repeal :","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"Watch McCain vote no 00:47","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"It 's not just Republicans who will have to recalibrate their thoughts on the tax bill","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"now that it 's a hybrid tax-health care plan .","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"The latest change could make it much harder to attract any Democratic support .","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"`` This is turning a tax bill into a health care bill , ''","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Sen. Ron Wyden , D-Oregon , yelled during a markup in the Senate finance committee Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"`` Republicans just ca n't help themselves , ''","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"`` They 're so determined to provide tax giveaways to the rich","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"that they 're willing to raise premiums on millions of middle-class Americans","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"and kick 13 million people off their health care . ''","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"While getting Democrats to sign on was always a longshot ,","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"moderate Democrats met with White House officials last week at the Library of Congress .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"The decision","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"to include the repeal of the individual mandate","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"will give Democrats a familiar arsenal of attack lines .","depth":5},{"id":135,"text":"In the days and weeks","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"since Republicans first unveiled their tax bill ,","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"Democrats have tried to attack it as a tax cut for the wealthy and a major blow to the country 's debt and deficit .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"Those talking points have failed to create the kind of grassroots groundswell","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"that was seen during the health care fight","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"when Republicans endured hours-long town halls","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"where individuals would come","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"and recount stories","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"about how repealing Obamacare would affect their daily lives .","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"But that may change now .","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"Re-introducing the repeal of the individual mandate also brings groups like AARP , doctors and major insurance companies out of the wood work","depth":5},{"id":146,"text":"to oppose the Republicans ' plan .","depth":5},{"id":147,"text":"On Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":148,"text":"just after Republicans announced","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"they would include a repeal of the individual mandate ,","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"a number of health groups stated their united opposition in a letter to Congress","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"Mnuchin pressed on Trump 's false tax claim","depth":5},{"id":153,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":4},{"id":154,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":5},{"id":155,"text":"Mnuchin pressed on Trump 's false tax claim","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"01:38","depth":4},{"id":157,"text":"The news of the Senate change Tuesday reverberated across Capitol Hill","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"where some House Republicans made a last-minute push","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"to try to convince their leadership to include a repeal of the individual mandate in the House-version of the bill , something","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"a few members had been pushing all along .","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"But , House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy signaled Tuesday night","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"that he did n't expect the House rules committee to make the change .","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"`` If it 's in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"then there 's the ability for conference , ''","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"McCarthy said .","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"you 'll see it in ours this week . '' The view in the House is that the Senate must prove first","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"it can actually pass a repeal of the individual mandate .","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"The House already voted for it","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"and passed it earlier this year .","depth":6},{"id":171,"text":"`` We did n't want to complicate tax reform","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"and make it harder","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"than it otherwise would be ,","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"and in fact , it was really ,","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"the Senate was the issue ,","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"so , we 're now seeing","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"if the Senate has the votes","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"to actually repeal the individual mandates , ''","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan said on a Fox News town hall Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"`` This is totally different than health care , ''","depth":5},{"id":181,"text":"Kennedy said .","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"`` Nobody is standing up","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"and saying ,","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"'If you do this ,","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"I 'm not going to vote for the bill . '","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"There has been none of that .","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"Everyone wants to get to yes . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":375,"left":338,"